    <articleReference>
      <Value><![CDATA[Dr. Jan Magnus Bjordal, Mark I. Johnson, Vegard Iversen, Flavio Aimbire, and Rodrigo Alvaro Brandao Lopes-Martins. Photomedicine and Laser Surgery. April 2006, 24(2): 158-168. doi:10.1089/pho.2006.24.158.]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Low-Level Laser Therapy in Acute Pain: A Systematic Review of Possible Mechanisms of Action and Clinical Effects in Randomized Placebo-Controlled Trials]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
